019-07-22T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd94553d61b4221a51aa42be63cc9c2a5e75745","tid":1347812,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"ab35f04c3f4904064ab650566e258e8d79e028b7","tid":1347812,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"全港十八區<br />\n無一幸免"},{"pid":"5e03e720fb8bf8bf34d1533331e658bc73de528e","tid":1347812,"uid":36742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"937a5350276bba2f79fd66af17df6ee566b4e88b","tid":1347812,"uid":35849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:51:13.000Z","msg":"屯門學校聯網區主席打電話去警署問，確認3點鐘元朗會有事發生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"屌好撚癲，用黑社會黎分區戒嚴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721 警黑之夜 - 整合 (上環 + 元朗)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！<br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7338603552ebd626b8c5afe4834ea7ee327eb447","tid":1347812,"uid":95501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1af4e94b8616b9dca3ae50f071a495684177e11","tid":1347812,"uid":198418,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:50:16.000Z","msg":"27一齊出黎斬撚牛屎佬全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:52.000Z","msg":"大家小心,吾普比林鄭成功將一個政治事件轉為民眾打鬥事件,然後派軍警鎮壓"},{"pid":"231e4bbc002d23142bf625ec55581bb40376a007","tid":1347812,"uid":216800